# Pattern Evaluation

- Evaluation date: 2026-03-23 (America/Chicago)
- Total classes counted: 31 (30 domain POCOs + 1 static seed container)
- Patterns identified: 0
- Pattern density: 0 / 31 = 0.00
- Overall grade (decoupling & SOLID): D
  - Rationale: In-memory data wired directly in API endpoints; no interfaces or abstractions around data access; domain types are anemic DTOs; no inversion of control for persistence/validation/authorization; single `Program.cs` hosts everything; no SRP/ISP enforcement. Small scope mitigates risk slightly, preventing an F.

