## Improvement opportunities
- Introduce repository pattern (interfaces + implementations) for accounts, portfolios, and transactions; inject via DI.
- Add services/use-cases (e.g., `ITransactionService`) to separate HTTP transport from domain logic and enable testing.
- Define interfaces for compliance checks/alerting (Strategy for risk scoring, Observer for audit trail).
- Apply DTOs/validators and map to domain entities to enforce SRP and validate inputs.
- Split API composition into controllers or endpoint classes; move sample data to seed scripts or in-memory provider registered in DI.
